Package com.qubecell.beans

Class Summary
BaseBean The BaseBean class is to be extended by all the bean classes.
EventChargeBean The EventChargeBean class is used to store event charge parameter values which is sent to server.
EventChargeRespBean The EventChargeRespBean class is used to receive eventCharge command response.
MsisdnBean The MsisdnBean class is used to store MSISDN command parameter values.
MsisdnRespBean The MsisdnRespBean class is used to hold the msisdn response from server.
ResponseBaseBean  
SendOTPBean The SendOTPBean class is used to store OTP send request parameter information.
SendOTPRespBean The SendOTPRespBean class is used to receive sendOTP command response.
SubscribeBean The SubscribeBean class is used to store subscribe command information which is to be sent to server.
ValidateOTPBean The ValidateOTPBean class is used to store validate OTP request parameter details.
ValidateOTPRespBean The ValidateOTPRespBean class is used to receive validateOTP command response.
